{"textPanel":{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p>探究铜片在空气中灼烧后发生的变化</p>\n"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p>氧气的化学性质比较活泼，加热条件下若与金属铜发生化学反应则会生成氧化铜，氧化铜可与稀盐酸、稀硫酸反应生成铜盐，使溶液呈蓝色。</p>\n"},{"title":"用品","data":"<p>器材：蜡烛，火柴，酒精灯，坩埚钳，试管，抽纸</p>\n\n<p>药品：光亮的铜片，稀硫酸</p>\n"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p>(1) 点燃蜡烛，用坩埚钳夹住铜片，在蜡烛火焰上方对铜片进行烟熏，注意不要让铜片接触蜡烛火焰，观察现象，一段时间后，取下铜片，用抽纸擦拭铜片表面，观察现象。</p>\n\n<p>(2) 点燃酒精灯，用坩埚钳夹住铜片，在酒精灯火焰上灼烧铜片，观察现象，一段时间后，取下铜片，用抽纸擦拭铜片表面，观察现象。</p>\n\n<p>(3) 取在酒精灯火焰上灼烧后的铜片，在烧杯中倒入适量稀硫酸溶液，将灼烧后的铜片放入烧杯中，观察现象。</p>\n"},{"title":"现象","data":"<p>在蜡烛上烟熏的铜片表面变黑，用抽纸擦拭表面，黑色物质被擦去；在酒精灯上灼烧的铜片表面变黑，用抽纸擦拭表面，黑色物质不能被擦去。</p>\n\n<p>铜片表面黑色物质逐渐溶解，溶液由无色变为蓝色。</p>\n"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":400},"chemData":{"chemBackGroundColor":3422529,"viewStack":{"x":190.66791718104344,"y":-64.48048308994152,"scaleX":1,"scaleY":1},"children":[{"x":1446.4947156151457,"y":1148.3740631614396,"rotation":0,"index":0,"name":"TissueBox","uuid":"4211624484933345","addedNode":[],"currentPlugCurValue":null,"currentArea":null,"plugAnimation":false,"fun":false,"holdAnimation":false,"scaleX":1,"scaleY":1,"areaWasFullAry":[],"constructorAttribute":{"dataBuild":true},"medicineData":null,"bringToFront":true,"instanceName":"main.aid.TissueBox^1","dataVersion":7,"canCheckPure":true,"children":[]},{"temp":25,"voMol":0.01,"x":812.1008950090064,"y":797.2626441259488,"rotation":0,"index":1,"name":"Candle","uuid":"25693663316561643","addedNode":[],"currentPlugCurValue":null,"currentArea":null,"plugAnimation":false,"fun":false,"holdAnimation":false,"scaleX":1,"scaleY":1,"areaWasFullAry":[],"constructorAttribute":{"dataBuild":true},"medicineData":{"liquid":[],"solid":{"C25H52":{"dat":{"id":"313","name_cn":"蜡烛","type_cn":"固体","chemical":"C25H52","type":"block","heat_vaporization":40800,"gas_heat_capacity":7,"heat_capacity":"4200","Available":"0","density_solid":0.9,"density_liquid":0.75,"density_gas":0.002,"molecular_mass":352,"melting_point":51,"boiling_point":158,"color":"0xff0000","solubility":0},"mol":0.01}},"gas":[],"temp":25,"ion":[],"diss